    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within the defined acceptance band at all five operating points, supporting the conclusion that the model is fit for the intended COU.",
